The drama and naughtiness in the Big Brother Naija 2018 house continued today as returning housemate, Khloe claimed she has seen six used condoms since she returned to the house on Sunday. Khloe who had been previously disqualified from the house with his then partner K-brule made the revelation to fellow housemates, Rico Swavey and Cee-c. She also went ahead to suggest Miracle and Nina are responsible for it. “I have seen six used condoms in this house since Sunday I returned. The condoms used by Miracle and Nina in this house are too much. “I have seen many. I can’t lie, you can ask Tobi. “I’m not joking. I saw them on the staircase.”  Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook